    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crystalone is a Turn-based RPG inspired by the classics where you command your party to defeat enemies in addition to side-scrolling view in the exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player will meet dozens of original characters each with their own stories in the world and with different abilities and skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/c508c642d03de8dc21f59d953131ee51.poster.avif?t=1736453935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/c508c642d03de8dc21f59d953131ee51.webm?t=1736453935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/c508c642d03de8dc21f59d953131ee51.mp4?t=1736453935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >9 playable characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet and befriend 9 characters, discover their stories, help them and grow your bond together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character has a unique personality, role and abilities that are crucial in paving your way forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/87a938fc39a0916d39a895f9f77d1be3.poster.avif?t=1736453935\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/87a938fc39a0916d39a895f9f77d1be3.webm?t=1736453935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Celestial Phases</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic turn-based combat that players love with our additional mechanic that alters the strategic flow of combat into three phases Sol ,Luna and Stella. Each one will favor and strengthen types of actions over others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/cc64de2e327ff187d4d1f0791c0de579.poster.avif?t=1736453935\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/cc64de2e327ff187d4d1f0791c0de579.webm?t=1736453935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/cc64de2e327ff187d4d1f0791c0de579.mp4?t=1736453935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A World Filled with Secrets and Treasures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-crafted world that consists of eight main locations each with its own unique environments, weather, enemies and narrative story-telling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/1c6f03982b84d93949581119e366b5f1.poster.avif?t=1736453935\" width=644 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/1c6f03982b84d93949581119e366b5f1.webm?t=1736453935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148800/extras/1c6f03982b84d93949581119e366b5f1.mp4?t=1736453935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
